document_data.name: Gustaf
document_data.mainbody: '''Gustaf''' was a [[human]] who lived in [[Neverwinter]] in the late years of the 15{{Th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Relationships: Gustaf was a rival of his nearly identical twin brother, [[Rodrik]]. Gustaf was considered to be the "evil" brother.
document_data.Activities: As of [[1479 DR]], Gustaf was a regular of the [[Beached Leviathan]]. He was a purveyor of stolen goods and rare [[magic]], taking advantage on the tavern's popularity to make contacts for his illicit deals. Gustaf usually disguised himself as his brother to thwart Rodrik's plans to make him return to "the good path". He never raised his sword against his brother, however.
document_data.History: In 1479 DR, Gustaf located an entrance to [[Gauntlgrym]]. He sold that information to the [[Ashmadai]].{{cite dungeon/193/The Gauntlgrym Gambit}}
